n<ul>\n<li>凯美瑞</li>\n<li>帕萨特 20 款成绩优秀 18 款成绩极差</li>\n<li>亚洲龙</li>\n<li>领克</li>\n<li>天籁</li>\n</ul>\n<p>成绩差</p>\n<ul>\n<li>迈腾</li>\n<li>雅阁 </li>\n<li>君威</li>\n<li>英仕派</li>\n</ul>\n<p>不知道选哪一款</p>\n","last_modified":1691563844,"replies":34,"id":963755},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1689070442","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1689070442","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":57959,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1689070442","stars":8523,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":156669,"username":"javahuang","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/javahuang","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6da6bc14499fa6ff7af1d7e8b90e162a?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6da6bc14499fa6ff7af1d7e8b90e162a?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6da6bc14499fa6ff7af1d7e8b90e162a?s=73&d=retro","created":1453544911,"last_modified":1654181433},"last_reply_by":"790002517zzy","last_touched":1691579515,"title":"这样的人，我该帮他解决问题吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/963815","created":1691572169,"deleted":0,"content":"楼主开发了一个免费软件，经常有人进群寻求帮助，一般遇到客气的，我都乐意花时间帮他解决问题。\r\n但是经常也遇到这种连个礼貌用词都不带一个的，我该不该帮他们？\r\n\r\n![Imgur]( https://i.imgur.com/IGJJijd.png)","content_rendered":"<p>楼主开发了一个免费软件，经常有人进群寻求帮助，一般遇到客气的，我都乐意花时间帮他解决问题。\n但是经常也遇到这种连个礼貌用词都不带一个的，我该不该帮他们？</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Imgur\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IGJJijd.png\"/></p>\n","last_modified":1691572169,"replies":29,"id":963815},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.